nowhere near a restaurant.

00:07:16.790 --> 00:07:19.460
And, I realized I am living
out Steven King's misery.

00:07:19.460 --> 00:07:25.180
I am never going to see my
wife and daughter again.

00:07:25.180 --> 00:07:28.880
And, in the middle of
nowhere, we pull into a house.

00:07:28.880 --> 00:07:30.960
And, in all fairness,
it's a really nice house.

00:07:30.960 --> 00:07:33.120
We're talking serious medomansion.

00:07:33.120 --> 00:07:34.750
But, she gets out of
the car, and I'm sitting

00:07:34.750 --> 00:07:38.070
in the passenger seat
thinking do you text in 911.

00:07:38.070 --> 00:07:43.200
And, she says in her best Sandra
Bullock The Blindside voice well,

00:07:43.200 --> 00:07:44.500
are you coming.

00:07:44.500 --> 00:07:47.160
And, I realized I was a coming.

00:07:47.160 --> 00:07:49.850
So, I got out of the
car, I follow her

00:07:49.850 --> 00:07:52.030
into the garage and there's a door.

00:07:52.030 --> 00:07:56.980
And, I know that behind that door
is either a kitchen or a dungeon.

00:07:56.980 --> 00:07:59.950
We open the door and
yes, it's a kitchen.

00:07:59.950 --> 00:08:03.530
And, in there are four
guys in golf clothes.

00:08:03.530 --> 00:08:06.890
Two massive William snow
[inaudible] waffle makers.

00:08:06.890 --> 00:08:11.530
She's brought me to her house where
her husband, her brother in law,

00:08:11.530 --> 00:08:16.320
