Minnesota get together every week

00:08:16.320 --> 00:08:20.860
in October for golf and waffles.

00:08:20.860 --> 00:08:24.050
She welcomes me into
this wonderful man cave.

00:08:24.050 --> 00:08:27.650
And, her husband says
to me with a red bull

00:08:27.650 --> 00:08:30.250
and a green bull what would
you like on your waffles.

00:08:30.250 --> 00:08:33.780
We got ourselves pulled
pork and Cajun shrimp.

00:08:33.780 --> 00:08:38.090
And, I said I'm a blueberry
waffle man myself.

00:08:38.090 --> 00:08:43.550
And, his wife says George, I
told you, he's a vegetarian.

00:08:43.550 --> 00:08:46.960
At which point George -- and I'm
not making up one word of this --

00:08:46.960 --> 00:08:50.260
