accidently kill someone.

00:11:41.940 --> 00:11:45.190
Or, something far darker,
an adult serial killer

00:11:45.190 --> 00:11:48.750
who on a regular basis
murder small children.

00:11:48.750 --> 00:11:52.410
I was a child murderer.

00:11:52.410 --> 00:11:56.730
From those books, I learned so much

00:11:56.730 --> 00:11:59.460
