And, every day between
five and 7 a.m.

00:13:09.720 --> 00:13:12.780
in the morning I would
write fiction.

00:13:12.780 --> 00:13:18.020
I would write very F Scott
Fitzgerald short stories

00:13:18.020 --> 00:13:22.610
